<%- include("partials/header") %>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DMCA Policy | AniFusionStream</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Exact Obsidian Navy Color Palette */
        :root {
            --bg-deep: #0b0e11;      /* The darkest background */
            --navy-card: #151b23;    /* Main Navy Blue for containers */
            --navy-inner: #1c232d;   /* Darker Navy for sub-boxes and buttons */
            --primary-blue: #3b82f6;  /* Accent Electric Blue */
            --accent-purple: #a855f7; /* Accent Purple */
            --text-main: #ffffff;
            --text-dim: #9ca3af;
        }

        body { 
            background-color: var(--bg-deep); 
            color: var(--text-main); 
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        /* Forces everything to stay centered and tidy */
        .page-container {
            max-width: 680px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        /* The Main Navy Cards */
        .obsidian-card {
            background-color: var(--navy-card);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border-radius: 2.5rem; /* Matches the high roundness in your image */
            padding: 3rem;
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        /* Inner detail boxes with colored borders */
        .detail-box {
            background-color: var(--navy-inner);
            padding: 1.75rem;
            border-radius: 1.25rem;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
            border-left: 5px solid transparent;
        }

        .border-blue { border-left-color: var(--primary-blue); }
        .border-purple { border-left-color: var(--accent-purple); }

        .detail-box h3 {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .detail-box p {
            color: var(--text-dim);
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        /* Typography spacing */
        .intro-text {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .body-text {
            color: var(--text-dim);
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        /* Actions/Buttons in Navy Blue */
        .action-btn {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1.15rem;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.03em;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .btn-navy {
            background-color: var(--navy-inner);
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        .btn-blue {
            background-color: var(--primary-blue);
            color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
        }

        .action-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            filter: brightness(1.2);
        }

        .copyright-header {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .legal-footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #4b5563;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-style: italic;
            line-height: 1.8;
            padding: 0 1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="page-container">
        
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-4">
                DMCA <span class="text-blue-500">Policy</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-xl font-medium">
                Digital Millennium Copyright Act Notice
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="obsidian-card">
            <p class="intro-text">
                We respect the intellectual property rights of others and expect our users to do the same.
            </p>

            <div class="detail-box border-blue">
                <h3>No Hosted Content:</h3>
                <p>
                    We do not store any copyright-protected content on our servers. All posts are for educational and promotional purposes only. Any linked content is hosted on non-affiliated, third-party websites.
                </p>
            </div>

            <p class="body-text my-8">
                Content shown on <span class="text-white font-bold">AniFusionStream</span> is indexed from non-affiliated third-party sources—functioning similarly to how search engines operate. We do not directly host, upload, or control any of the video files.
            </p>

            <div class="detail-box border-purple">
                <h3>Promotional Use Only:</h3>
                <p>
                    This website is meant strictly for private use. All materials are shared solely for testing, introductory, and promotional purposes. We highly encourage all users to purchase official media directly from official sources to support the original creators and publishers.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="obsidian-card text-center">
            <h2 class="copyright-header">Copyright Infringement?</h2>
            <p class="body-text mb-10">
                If you are a copyright holder or a legal representative and believe your work has been posted without permission, please reach out to us with proof of ownership, and we will take prompt action.
            </p>

            <a href="mailto:anifusionstream@gmail.com" class="action-btn btn-navy">
                Email Directly
            </a>

            <a href="/contact-us" class="action-btn btn-blue">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7 8.941L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                </svg>
                Contact Form
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-footer">
            By continuing to browse this site, you affirm your understanding and compliance with this DMCA policy. All materials are believed to be in the public domain and are the property of their respective owners.
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>
<%- include("partials/footer") %>